OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIBM pulls X ads as content 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fseen beside pro-Nazi posts 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, IBM has suspended advertising on X,    
OL,6, formerly known as Twitter, after a     
OL,7, report said its ads were placed next to
OL,8, posts praising Adolf Hitler and Nazism.
OL,10,FThe company said it was "completely    
OL,11,Funacceptable" that its content appeared
OL,12,Fin such threads on the platform.       
OL,14,FX said it does not intentionally place 
OL,15,Fbrands "next to this kind of content". 
OL,17,FIt comes as X owner Elon Musk was      
OL,18,Fcriticised after calling an antisemitic
OL,19,Fconspiracy theory "actual truth" when  
OL,20,Freplying to a post on the platform.    
